ZH: 他一直守信用，从来没有欺骗过他人。
EN: He has always been trustworthy and never deceived anyone.

ZH: 她是一个守信用的生意人，经营了多年的公司信誉很好。
EN: She is a trustworthy businesswoman and has maintained a good reputation for her company over the years.

ZH: 他希望能找到一个守信用的供应商，以确保产品的质量和交货时间。
EN: He hopes to find a trustworthy supplier to ensure the quality and delivery time of the products.

ZH: 这家公司非常守信用，按时支付所有的员工工资。
EN: This company is very trustworthy and pays all its employees' wages on time.

ZH: 他们守信用，始终按照合同约定完成工程。
EN: They are trustworthy and always complete the projects as agreed in the contracts.

ZH: 守信用是一个企业最重要的品牌资产之一。
EN: Trustworthiness is one of the most important brand assets for a company.

ZH: 在商业交易中，守信用是建立长期合作的基础。
EN: Trustworthiness is the foundation for building long-term cooperation in business transactions.

ZH: 他的守信用的行为赢得了客户的赞赏和信任。
EN: His trustworthiness has earned him appreciation and trust from his clients.

ZH: 长期守信用将使企业积累良好的信誉和口碑。
EN: Long-term trustworthiness will enable a company to build a good reputation and public image.

ZH: 只有守信用的企业才能在竞争激烈的市场中立于不败之地。
EN: Only trustworthy companies can stand invincible in a fiercely competitive market.

ZH: 作为一个守信用的朋友，我会一直支持你。
EN: As a trustworthy friend, I will always support you.

ZH: 守信用是一个人品质的体现，也是衡量一个人是否可信任的重要指标。
EN: Trustworthiness is a reflection of a person's character and an important indicator of whether a person can be trusted.

ZH: 她向来守信用，从未食言。
EN: She has always been true to her word and never made false promises.

ZH: 守信用才能建立良好的人际关系。
EN: Trustworthiness is crucial for building good interpersonal relationships.

ZH: 无论遇到什么困难，他都会坚持守信用的原则。
EN: He will adhere to the principle of trustworthiness no matter what difficulties he encounters.

ZH: 守信用的人会为他人着想，不会轻易违背承诺。
EN: Trustworthy people consider others and will not easily break their promises.

ZH: 在国际贸易中，守信用是促进合作的重要保障。
EN: Trustworthiness is an important guarantee for promoting cooperation in international trade.

ZH: 他的守信用行为赢得了合作伙伴的信赖。
EN: His trustworthiness has gained the trust of his business partners.

ZH: 忠于承诺是守信用的基本要求之一。
EN: Being loyal to commitments is one of the basic requirements for trustworthiness.

ZH: 他希望通过守信用的行为来树立良好的个人形象。
EN: He hopes to establish a good personal image through trustworthy behavior.
